name: Film
description:
This shot was taken at a closed party in honor of Levis' new collection. 
There is a very talented guy who calls himself «18». He sings a song about a girl who is comparable to the Earth for him. 
Do you feel the energy of this shot? I had a lot of fun and comfort that night. The whole party was very homey and friendly.   
Every year I go to such events less and less, so their memory is very important to me
